WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Protect me today in all my travels along the road's way.

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Give me your warning sign if danger is near.

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:14.000
So that I may stop while the path is clear.

4
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Prayer of St. Christopher, Patron Saint of Travelers.

5
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Oh mom! Yeah!

6
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Do you really want to do something like this?

7
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Lucas! Lucas wake up!

8
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
What happened? Where are we?
